      "content": "that's a really solid start. it definitely hits those systemic points. i'm worried though that some people in class might try to argue that meritocracy is more important or that redistribution is \"unfair\" to people who worked hard. how should i address those counter-arguments in my essay? like, how can i show that the meritocracy argument doesn't really hold up in this context?",
